                <Gloss>the means of convincing</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to interpret πεισμονή in {S:04800500800004} as the actual process of persuasion, in which case πεισμονή would be classified as a nominal form corresponding to {L:πείθω&lt;SDBG:πείθω:000000&gt;}[a] ({D:33.301}). Such an interpretation would require one to render {S:04800500800004} as he who called you was not the one who persuaded you.</Comments>
